-- This is auto-generated code
SELECT TOP 100
*
FROM
    OPENROWSET(
        BULK 'https://nycanalyticsmarlabsdl.dfs.core.windows.net/nyc-taxi-data/raw/payment_type_array.json',
        FORMAT = 'CSV',
        FIELDQUOTE = '0x0b',
        FIELDTERMINATOR ='0x0b',
        ROWTERMINATOR = '0x0b'
    )
    WITH (
        jsonContent varchar(MAX)
    ) AS [result]
    CROSS APPLY OPENJSON(jsonContent)
    WITH
    (
        rate_code_id SMALLINT,
        rate_code VARCHAR(30)
    );
